tool_description: Sudoku solver and generator for 9x9 sudoku puzzles.
name: SudoQ
title: SudoQ

api_list.name: Puzzle generator
api_list.description: Generates puzzles in 4 of levels: easy, medium, hard, evil!
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://sudoq.p.rapidapi.com/generate/easy"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "sudoq.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
